# Browser support baseline for the RomM frontend. Matches Tailwind v4's
# minimum targets. This is the single source of truth for browser support:
# vite.config.js derives Lightning CSS's `build.cssTarget` from it (so the
# production build prefixes/down-levels CSS for exactly these browsers), and
# any other tooling reads the same file. Expressed as floors, not pinned
# versions, and the actual version data comes from caniuse-lite.
chrome >= 111
edge >= 111
firefox >= 128
safari >= 16.4
ios_saf >= 16.4
